article.description: — Taevion Kinsey had 28 points as Marshall topped Ohio 81-67 on Sunday.
article.headline: Kinsey scores 28 to carry Marshall over Ohio 81-67
article.linkText: Kinsey scores 28 to carry Marshall over Ohio 81-67
article.story: HUNTINGTON, W.Va. -- — Taevion Kinsey had 28 points as Marshall topped Ohio 81-67 on Sunday. Kinsey hit 10 of 13 shots. Jarrod West had 14 points for Marshall (4-0). Mikel Beyers added 13 points. Dwight Wilson III had 24 points for the Bobcats (4-2). Jason Preston added 19 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
